<p>In this post, I describe the setup procedure of this blog site.</p>

<p>This site is developed with Jekyll, a static site generator and hosted by Github pages. All contents of the site are registered in <a href="https://github.com/yumaloop/yumaloop.github.io">Github public repository</a> and you can browse any source code in it.</p>

